parameters: \n<Lyric>"...Peeping, huh? That's not exactly a noble hobby, is it?"

\n<Roselitte>"...Even though I erased my presence, you noticed me.
Impressive."

\n<Lyric>"Nfufu. Maybe your skills have dulled since you've been
sick."

\n<Roselitte>"Well, it's impossible to remain undetected by a succubus
who's always on guard."
\n<Roselitte>"I've put her to bed. She's sleeping with her mouth open."

\n<Lyric>"Putting her to bed... Can't she take care of herself? She's
not a child."
\n<Roselitte>"...Do you intend to stay up all night like this?"

\n<Lyric>"Yeah. We'll arrive at Annabern by tomorrow, right? Staying
up one night won't be a problem. Our bodies are more
resilient than you humans, after all."

\n<Lyric>"Just go to sleep without worrying. I'll keep an eye on our
surroundings, and since you probably don't like it, I won't
come any closer."

\n<Lyric>"Besides, you left Ameria in my care, and now you're peeping
instead of watching her? Are you stupid? It's dangerous, so
hurry back there, knight."

\n<Roselitte>"...Indeed. Then I will retire without further ado,
succubus."

\n<Roselitte>"Even though we're only traveling together until tomorrow,
it would be troublesome if you collapsed from lack of
sleep."
\n<Roselitte>"...Rest here. I'm also keeping watch around us."
